#20000
The Precipice~
You stand before the gates of the Lost Citadel.  The area has been decimated, 
the walls of the citadel are blackened and charred.  The ground you stand on 
extends out from the citadel half a dozen yards, then is swallowed up by mist.  
All around you is the stench of death.
~
