#20001
The Entrance Chamber~
You stand within the gates of the Lost Citadel.  A dull light seems to emanate 
from the very walls.  The citadel is crafted out of a beautiful black marble, 
that has blood red veins running through it.  Massive pillars run the length of 
the room.  As you look at them, their tops, as well as the ceiling are lost 
in shadows.
~
