#20042
The Ethereal Edge~
You are standing in a swirling storm of mist.  You cannot see what is supporting 
Your feet, yet it seems solid.  Through the torrent of chaos about you, you catch 
glimpses of other places, and possibly other times.  You feel close to a power,
something of great malevolence, and cunning.  Yet nothing revels its self 
to you.
~
